    "In fact, some participants in the study reported various discomforts when wearing eye-tracking glasses and EMG armbands.",
    "They also reported slightly different experiences when sporting sensors during badminton motion than when not wearing any.",
    "Therefore, after collecting such data, it is essential to conduct additional research to reduce the number of sensors by analyzing the correlations between them.",
